OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter body recovered from roof fire
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder after a body was recovered
OL,8,Ffrom a roof fire on the Isle of Wight.
OL,10,FThe 28-year-old from Ventnor has also
OL,11,Fbeen accused of arson with intent to
OL,12,Fendanger life, Hampshire & Isle of
OL,13,FWight Police said.
OL,15,FFirefighters were called to a fire,
OL,16,Fwhich tore through the roofs of three
OL,17,Fproperties, at Ronsons Close, in
OL,18,FCowes, in the early hours of Friday
OL,19,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
