OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter body recovered from roof fire
OL,6,FA body was subsequently located by
OL,7,Fcrews.
OL,9,FIt has yet to be formally identified,
OL,10,Fbut the individual's next of kin have
OL,11,Fbeen informed, police added.
OL,13,FThey are being supported by specialist
OL,14,Fofficers and a file will be prepared
OL,15,Ffor the coroner
OL,17,FAround 30 firefighters attended the
OL,18,Ffire, alongside an aerial ladder
OL,19,Fplatform.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
