OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter body recovered from roof fire
OL,6,FThe cause of it has not yet been
OL,7,Fconfirmed, but police are treating it
OL,8,Fas suspicious.
OL,10,FOfficers from the force will maintain
OL,11,Fa presence in the area in the coming
OL,12,Fdays whilst enquiries are conducted.
